# Cyrus
# ─────
# Streaming session logs (huge, regenerable from replay).
missions/*/[0-9]*-live.*
missions/*/tails/

# Per-iteration bookkeeping (durable trajectory is in ledger.md + summary.md
# + checklist.json; per-iter task/result/review is replayable from session).
missions/*/[0-9]*-task.md
missions/*/[0-9]*-result.md
missions/*/[0-9]*-review.md
missions/*/[0-9]*-intervention.md
missions/*/[0-9]*-notice.json
missions/*/[0-9]*-notice.stale-*.json

# Process locks and heartbeats (machine-specific, ephemeral).
missions/*/.lock
missions/*/.driving

# Diagnostic envelopes (large, debugging only).
missions/*/diagnostics/

# Verbatim user pastes — may contain secrets/paths/API logs.
# Remove this line to commit user evidence with the mission.
missions/*/inbox/

# Planning-phase uploads (screenshots, PDFs, attached binaries).
# Remove this line to commit attached reference material with the mission.
missions/*/attachments/

# Workspace event log (useful locally, grows forever).
log.jsonl

# Doer pre-consult worktree — full HEAD checkout, temporary.
.consult-*/
